This paper deals with natural language processing tasks related to citation analysis, specifically citation function and provenance prediction. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.CL (Computation and Language), which deals with the intersection of computer science and linguistics. The paper also uses machine learning techniques, which suggests sub-categories such as cs.IR (Information Retrieval), cs.LG (Machine Learning), and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Finally, the paper uses convolutional neural networks, which suggests the sub-category cs.DL (Deep Learning).
